# Advanced CSS3 & Responsive Architecture

This project demonstrates modern CSS3 concepts, including Flexbox, CSS Grid, media queries, and responsive web design techniques. The website adapts smoothly to mobile, tablet, and desktop devices.

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- Flexbox
- CSS Grid
- Media Queries

## Features
- Responsive design
- Mobile-first approach
- Flexible layouts
- Modern UI design
